title: Ep 8: The Streets Don't Wait
itunes:title: Ep 8: The Streets Don't Wait
description: Episode 8 starts out with an apology for its delay but these streets wait for no one and Shannon is really in the throws of them. The girls discuss how AG nearly escapes death of the Gin variety and what sexual endeavors shouldn't be done while driving. Talking during sex? Into it. Talking to your penis out loud after sex? Ehhhh. Shannon has yet another Raya story but this one was less interested in her and more into her medical record. Which hit show's leading man did she cross paths with in New York? How to say F U to a man who belittles your career and which red flags they've experienced and fallen for in the past. All of this and more explained in "The Streets Don't Wait"
